records.addlTxt: Preliminary hearing on November 11, 2022 at 09:00 am.

[ae] case called 8:49 AM Defendant Erin M McVeigh appeared by phone. ADA Michaels in court for State of Wisconsin. 
The Defendant verifies that the date of birth listed on the Criminal Complaint is correct and provides current mailing address

Preliminary Hearing time limits are waived by both parties.

The Court requires $2,500 Signature Bond, with conditions:
--not to use or possess any financial or transactional documents other than her own
--not to discuss the case with with co-defendant, may have contact regarding child placement and other decisions regarding child.
--Defendant is to report to the Jefferson County Sheriff's Office for booking (fingerprints and photographs)
--Defendant is to sign bond by 4:00 pm on 10/07/22

The Court informs the Defendant failure to appear to sign bond will result in the issuance of a warrant
